sections.heading: park system; classification of areas
sections.text: The commission shall periodically evaluate and assess the state park system by classifications and may redesignate specific areas from one class to another.SourceLaws 1959, c. 436, ยง 4, p. 1466;R.S.1943, (1996), ยง 81-815.24;Laws 1998, LB 922, ยง 98.
